Missing Sanele Butsaka. Multimedia &nbsp; &nbsp; User Galleries &nbsp; &nbsp; News in Pictures Send us your pictures &nbsp; &nbsp; Send us your stories The family of Sanele Butsaka who went missing in December 2016 are desperately looking for him.The 17 year old was last seen on December 8 after he was allegedly taken away by two men driving a Silver Toyota Quest. He was last seen wearing black Gugs bomber jacket and a black Gutter pant. A reward of R90 000 has been offered to anyone that my have information of his whereabouts. Contact Sandile on 0747854733/0719374942. 24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.